{"tid":991280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【大浪冚濕身】水警西貢大灣執勤遇險 直升機救起送院命危","createTime":"2019-01-22T09:09:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T18:15:08.000Z","uid":122068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d330bd1f3f77f306a5f125efec975f497c6733d3","tid":991280,"uid":122068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T09:09:24.000Z","msg":"【16:05】水警經搶救後情況危殆<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，早上約11時，一名水警在西貢大灣，與同袍執行職務，其間須在海邊涉水而行，據悉當時現場天氣寒冷海水冰冷，<span style=\"color: red;\">突然間一個大浪沖上岸，水警當場遇險，懷疑受傷又或是遇溺 </span>。同袍見狀通報上級，由於大灣較偏遠，政府飛行服務隊遂奉召到場，把該名水警送往東區醫院搶救，目前情況危殆，留醫深切治療部。事後水警的家屬接獲通知趕至醫院，另有一名水警總督察亦到場了解事件。<br />\n <a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190122/59170625/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190122%2F59170625%2F&d=4cMhME4%2F8xdsHij0ahPe49tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=24a1731a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190122%2F59170625%2F&h=801c205a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190122/59170625/</a>"},{"pid":"075735ce0604ba32099dd5f972a660d542302ec2","tid":991280,"uid":103914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T09:11:43.000Z","msg":"執行職務定蛇王呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5349430d53cb51bb1bba480b61c373b43aa2786e","tid":991280,"uid":202278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T18:15:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}